### List all cases
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases

### List cases with search
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases?search=test

### List cases with pagination
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases?page=1&page_size=10

### Create a new case
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Case",
  "description": "A test case for verifying the API"
}

### Create a case without description
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Minimal Case"
}

### Get a case by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}

### Update a case
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Case Name",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Update only the case name
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Renamed Case"
}

### Delete a case
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}

### Add documents to a case
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_ids": ["{{document_id}}"]
}

### List documents in a case
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}/documents

### List documents in a case with pagination
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}/documents?page=1&page_size=10

### Remove a document from a case
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/cases/{{case_id}}/documents/{{document_id}}
